products.title: Dress
products.description: Wanna bring the heat? Look fire from the ground up in this flattering midi skirt. Sitting midway down the calf and skimming your hips for a flattering fit, mid-length skirts are the wardrobe hero you need in your life this season. This on-trend piece is your go-to style for versatility, and is renowned for its complimentary fit. Just pair with trainers for the perfect casual look, or swap out your flats for heels and your Saturday night glam is sorted.  95% Polyester and 5% Elastane. Machine Washable. Model Wears UK Size 10

products.title: dress
products.description: Wanna make a statement? Shine like the star you are in this sequin skirt. Perfect for all upcoming nights out and party celebrations, a sequin skirt is a wardrobe staple that can be worn year on year without fail. Because who doesn’t love a sequin or two? Pair with statement heels and a matching bodysuit and you’re ready to shine, girl. From sequin mini skirts to midi styles, we’ve got it all…because you can never have too much sparkle in your life, right?  95% Polyester 5% Elastane. Model wears size 10.

products.title: HOODIE
products.description: Wanna keep things comfy? Jump on the oversized trend with this men's oversized hoodie from our latest collection. With a relaxed fit and a hood attached to the neckline, we're talking all over comfort all. season. long. Wear with joggers and slides for off-duty days or team with paint splatter jeans and a shacket for a look we love.  50% Cotton (25% is Recycled), 50% Polyester (25% is Recycled).
